[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Virtual reality, can it be used for traditional art? It was a couple months ago where some Instagram reel was just really popping off showing this artist using VR to start a mural. I got DM\'d that reel probably 25 30 times. But'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'something stuck in the back of my brain like that is pretty cool. I should try that out eventually. Well, that eventually is today. Also, simultaneously, another YouTuber named The Good Chad reached out to me and'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'shared his video using VR for his art. And that was very informative and gave me a basis of like how this technology actually works. I have, what is this? A Quest 2. I\'ve had this for a while. I\'ve used it probably three times. But for'

[00:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this video specifically, I went out and bought the MetaQuest 3S, which is the upgrade to this. And that\'s mostly because the pass through cameras on this are in full color and they\'re much higher quality than this. Quick side'

[00:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'note, I forgot to mention in that other recording, I\'m not sponsored by the MetaQuest 3S or the apps that I\'m going to be using in this video. I paid for those with my own money. Nobody asked me to do this. I just wanted to try this'

