VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'out. So, not sponsored. I mean, this video does have a sponsor. That\'s Squarespace, but we\'ll talk about that later. Okay, back to it. What I\'d like to do is try and use VR to start a mural. We have a little wall over here,'

[01:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and I want to see if it would work on a smaller canvas like a painting. Could this eliminate the use of transfer paper? Could this eliminate the use of traditional grids, of doodle grids, of projectors, which have a whole host of'

[01:30] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'problems like having to use them at night, having to have enough distance from your wall. We\'re going to find all that out today. and I\'m going to find out if I can implement VR into my traditional art process. Let\'s get started. Okay, first things first, I'

